title: [Vornavian Coast, The Lake]
description: Several large rocks lie partly in the lake to the north here, providing a nice place to dive from or to sit and gaze at the stars above.  A picnic basket with a broken handle has been discarded near the rocks, and ants nearly encase the basket, crawling in and out looking for a meal.

Several large rocks lie partly in the lake to the north here, providing a nice place to dive from or to sit and absorb the midday sun.  A picnic basket with a broken handle has been discarded near the rocks, and ants nearly encase the basket, crawling in and out looking for a meal.
